  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: Order of the Profane Soul</em></p><p>When a creature you can see within 30 feet of you ends it's turn without moving, you can use your reaction to prevent it from taking the same Action and Bonus action until the end of the creature's next turn.<br /><br /><strong>Amplify</strong>. This curse lasts up to 1 minute, and whenever the creature makes the Action or Bonus action prevent by the curse on it's turn ends it takes force damage equal to one roll of your hemocraft die plus your Intelligence modifier (minimum of 1). Starting after the end of the creature's next turn, the cursed creature can make a Charisma saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the curse on itself on a success.<br /></p>",
